r, score, reserve, permit, and bind pods\n\n## Supporting Data Structures\n`pkg/scheduler/framework/cycle_state.go`: Maintains state during a single scheduling cycle\n`pkg/scheduler/framework/types.go`: Defines core types like NodeScore, NodeInfo, and CycleState\n\nThe architecture follows a plugin-based design pattern where the frameworkImpl coordinates plugin execution at well-defined extension points throughout the scheduling cycle. Each plugin type (Filter, Score, Bind, etc.) represents a specific decision point in the scheduler's workflow."
